HEADWORD: matchboard
<hw>matchboard</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A board that has a groove cut
into one edge and a tongue cut into the other so they fit tightly
together (as in a floor); see <cref>match boarding</cref>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

